6.4, 947.1]}, {"text": "Notes to Five-Year Financial Summary", "bbox": [56.3, 974.7, 323.4, 991.4]}, {"text": "a.", "bbox": [56.3, 993.9, 72.0, 1010.7]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2011 included an $11 million non-operating gain related to the sale of interest in an equity method investment and a $21 million reduction to income tax", "bbox": [92.5, 993.9, 1158.3, 1010.7]}, {"text": "expense related to a reversal of reserves for foreign uncertain tax positions.", "bbox": [92.5, 1012.9, 597.8, 1029.7]}, {"text": "b.", "bbox": [56.3, 1032.2, 73.0, 1048.9]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2010 included $61 million of interest expense related to losses on notes repurchased/redeemed during fiscal 2010, a $29 million non-tax deductible", "bbox": [92.5, 1032.2, 1122.8, 1048.9]}, {"text": "charge related to a full goodwill impairment related to an immaterial Chicken segment reporting unit and a $12 million non-operating charge related to the", "bbox": [92.5, 1051.4, 1128.3, 1068.2]}, {"text": "partial impairment of an equity method investment. Additionally, fiscal 2010 included insurance proceeds received of $38 million related to Hurricane Katrina.", "bbox": [92.5, 1070.4, 1159.6, 1087.2]}, {"text": "c.", "bbox": [56.3, 1089.7, 72.0, 1106.5]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2009 was a 53-week year, while the other years presented were 52-week years.", "bbox": [92.5, 1089.7, 667.8, 1106.5]}, {"text": "d.", "bbox": [56.3, 1109.0, 73.0, 1125.7]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2009 included a $560 million non-tax deductible charge related to Beef segment goodwill impairment and a $15 million pretax charge related to closing", "bbox": [92.5, 1109.0, 1155.8, 1125.7]}, {"text": "a prepared foods plant.", "bbox": [92.5, 1128.0, 249.6, 1144.7]}, {"text": "e.", "bbox": [56.3, 1147.2, 72.0, 1164.0]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2008 included $76 million of pretax charges related to: restructuring a beef operation; closing a poultry plant; asset impairments for packaging", "bbox": [92.5, 1147.2, 1091.5, 1164.0]}, {"text": "equipment, intangible assets, unimproved real property and software; flood damage; and severance charges. Additionally, fiscal 2008 included an $18 million", "bbox": [92.5, 1166.5, 1149.3, 1183.2]}, {"text": "non-operating gain related to the sale of an investment.", "bbox": [92.5, 1185.5, 463.9, 1202.2]}, {"text": "f.", "bbox": [56.3, 1204.7, 70.2, 1221.5]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2007 included tax expense of $17 million related to a fixed asset tax cost correction, primarily related to a fixed asset system conversion in 1999.", "bbox": [92.5, 1204.7, 1108.6, 1221.5]}, {"text": "g.", "bbox": [56.3, 1224.0, 73.0, 1240.7]}, {"text": "Return on invested capital is calculated by dividing operating income (loss) by the sum of the average of beginning and ending total debt and shareholders’", "bbox": [92.5, 1224.0, 1132.1, 1240.7]}, {"text": "equity less cash and cash equivalents.", "bbox": [92.5, 1243.1, 347.6, 1259.8]}, {"text": "h.", "bbox": [56.3, 1262.3, 73.0, 1279.1]}, {"text": "For the total debt to capitalization calculation, capitalization is defined as total debt plus total shareholders’ equity.", "bbox": [92.5, 1262.3, 861.7, 1279.1]}, {"text": "i.", "bbox": [56.3, 1281.6, 69.2, 1298.3]}, {"text": "In March 2009, we completed the sale of the beef processing, cattle feed yard and fertilizer assets of three of our Alberta, Canada subsidiaries (collectively,", "bbox": [92.5, 1281.6, 1133.4, 1298.3]}, {"text": "Lakeside). Lakeside was reported as a discontinued operation for all periods presented.", "bbox": [92.5, 1300.6, 676.8, 1317.3]}]}